							<div class="section-content-container">
								<h2 class="section-title alt section-title-animate" aria-label="Sustainability">
									<span aria-hidden="true">Sustain<span class="ability">ability</span></span>
								</h2>
								<p class="section-subtitle">Securing the future of our industry</p>
								<p>More than any other health insurance company in Iowa and South Dakota, Wellmark Blue Cross and Blue Shield has the ability to sustain our health care system—by containing rising costs while enhancing service, educating consumers, and encouraging healthy living for our members and communities. To achieve this sustainability imperative, we actively affect transformation both inside and outside the health care system.</p>
