			<div class="section-measureability">
				<div class="section-content-container">
					<div class="container-fluid">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-md-5">
								<h2 class="section-title section-title-animate" aria-label="Measureability">
									<span aria-hidden="true">Measur<span class="ability">ability</span></span>
								</h2>
								<p class="section-subtitle">Quantifying quality</p>
								<p>Just like a <em>Consumer Reports®</em> score, Wellmark’s Value Index Score quantifies the quality of health care provided by a primary care physician. Launched in 2012 and comprised of 18 quality measures, the score helps members understand how well physicians manage their entire patient population. Today, the score is available to Wellmark members on the myWellmark® Care Finder—for more than 1,400 primary care physicians. The five-point scale allows for easy comparison of doctors.</p>		
							</div>
							<div class="col-md-7">
								<div class="infographic text-center infographic-animate">
									<img class="laptop center-block img-hd" src="<%= config.assetPath %>img/ceo/laptop-quality-score-2x.png" alt="" />							
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
