								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="col-md-6">
								<div class="center-block text-center content-shop-compare last">
									<img class="iconography img-hd predict-iconography-animate" src="<%= config.assetPath %>img/ceo/iconography/care-finder@2x.png" alt="" />
									<h3 id="predictabilityHeader2">Shop and compare</h3>
									<p>Transparency can help shape the future of health care.</p>
									<button type="button" class="btn btn-link light learn-more" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#care-finder-modal" aria-describedby="predictabilityHeader2">
										Learn More
