				<img src="<%= config.assetPath %>img/ceo/outside-hc-system.jpg" alt="" />
				<div class="card">
					<h2 class="section-title" aria-label="Outside the Health Care System">
						<span aria-hidden="true">Outside the<br /> Health Care System</span>
					</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="arrow-down" aria-hidden="true"></div>
			</div>

			<div class="section-improvability">
				<div class="section-content-container">
					<div class="container-fluid">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-md-7">
								<div class="section-improvability-copy">
									<h2 class="section-title section-title-animate" aria-label="Improvability">
										<span aria-hidden="true">Improv<span class="ability">ability</span></span>
									</h2>
									<p class="section-subtitle">Making your hometown an even better place to live</p>
									<p>Research proves our behaviors and environment make up 70 percent of the factors influencing our overall health. In Iowa and South Dakota, experts estimate that by 2030, 1 in 4 people will have heart disease, and 1 in 8 will be diabetic. It’s time to do something about it.</p>
									<p>Enter Healthy Hometown<sup>SM</sup> Powered By Wellmark—a program that makes your hometown an even better place to live. It offers proven tools for communities to make long-lasting changes, transforming their environments and making the healthy choice the easy choice.</p>
									<p>Iowa communities can start their journey toward even better living at <a href="http://www.iowahealthieststate.com/" target="_blank">IowaHealthiestState.com<span class="sr-only">External Site</span></a><span class="icon-wmkExternalLinkSmall" aria-hidden="true"></span>.</p>
									<p>In South Dakota, look for more information soon!</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="col-md-5">
								<img class="center-block logo-healthy-hometown img-hd infographic-animate" src="<%= config.assetPath %>img/ceo/healthy-hometown@2x.png" alt="" />
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="arrow-down gray" aria-hidden="true"></div>
			</div>

			<div class="section-outro">
				<img src="<%= config.assetPath %>img/ceo/river-flow.jpg" alt="" />
				<div class="card">
					<h2 class="section-title">What sets us apart</h2>
					<p>We are a mutual insurance company. We answer to our members, not investors. We’re here and listening—always improving the system and clearing the way to quality, affordable health care.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

