					<p>For 2017 we collaborated with Mercy Health Network and the University of Iowa Health System to create two new health insurance companies committed to managing the care of our members. These new health insurance companies serve 44 Iowa counties and allow us to offer high quality insurance products with select provider networks.  Quality care is delivered more effectively through a carefully managed network, all with the goal of reducing the total cost of care.</p>
